desc.en: Jialidun Metro is the author's own fantasy of a subway line at home. At present, a total of six lines and 90 stations are in operation. Fun and fantasy city battles are its characteristics. More subway lines will be updated in the future, stay tuned!(Material comes from Baidu and Tiktok)
desc.zh: 家里蹲地铁是本作者自己幻想的在家里的地铁线路。目前共运营6条线路和90座车站。趣味性和换乘站多是它的特色。未来还将更新更多地铁线路，敬请期待（素材来源于百度和抖音）
